[node name="RichTextLabel" type="RichTextLabel" parent="HelpScreen/CenterContainer/VBoxContainer/HBoxContainer" unique_id=852465308]
custom_minimum_size = Vector2(400, 0)
layout_mode = 2
size_flags_vertical = 4
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Welcome to Threat Level!

In this game you play as an experiment created in an underground lab.
Now you have escaped your confines and are ready to kill your creators.

[b]The goal:[/b] Make it to the top of the building and take out the Boss

To do this you must spawn and mutate your way, stealing the human's precious [b]BIOMASS[/b] to fuel your [b]THING[/b]s.

"
fit_content = true

[node name="RichTextLabel2" type="RichTextLabel" parent="HelpScreen/CenterContainer/VBoxContainer/HBoxContainer" unique_id=1486940279]
custom_minimum_size = Vector2(400, 0)
layout_mode = 2
size_flags_vertical = 4
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]Controls:[/b]
Camera Movement - WASD or Middle mouse + drag
Camera Zoom - Scroll wheel
Select [b]THING[/b] - Click
Apply Mutation - Click
Pause - Space
Menu - Esc

[b]Tips:[/b]
- Your first [b]THING[/b] will have no way of walking, try giving it legs, or spawning from it.
- If your [b]THING[/b]s arent behaving as you want, try some different mutations, some may change their behavior.
- Try out different combinations of mutations to see what works best!

"
fit_content = true

